data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home boasts a classic front porch exuding warmth and character, complemented by a new front door that welcomes you inside. Stepping in, a spacious, open-concept layout unfolds, featuring a generously sized living room, seamlessly flowing into a gracious dining room making it perfect for gatherings. The well-appointed eat-in kitchen showcases gleaming stainless steel appliances. One of the bedrooms is graced by a charming bay window, adding a touch of elegance and natural light to the space. This home offers a full-size unfinished basement, providing ample potential for customization and additional living space to suit your needs. A deck extends from the rear, overlooking a large, fully fenced backyard with half privacy fence, offering a tranquil oasis for relaxation and entertaining. A convenient shed provides extra storage space for tools or outdoor equipment. Noteworthy upgrades include new windows in the back bedroom, living room, kitchen, and basement, ensuring energy efficiency and enhanced aesthetics. The addition of AC vents throughout the house ensures optimal comfort in all seasons. Further improvements encompass new insulation in the attic, reinforcing energy efficiency, and added supports under the house, enhancing structural integrity. This property includes the added convenience of a washer and dryer, simplifying your day-to-day chores. The AC/HVAC system and roof were both replaced in 2022, showcasing recent upgrades that offer peace of mind for years to come.
